message.content: def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ := Nat.greatestDivisor x (fun d => d % 2 = 1)

def greatestOddDivisor : ℕ → ℕ :=
  λ n, n.divisors.filter (λ d, d % 2 = 1) |>.sup

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  Nat.gcd x (2 * x - 1)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  Nat.find_greatest (λ d, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x
def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ := x.divisors.filter (λ d : ℕ, d % 2 = 1) |>.max' (by simp [Nat.one_dvd, Nat.dvd_refl])
def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ := x.divisors.filter (λ d, d % 2 = 1).max'

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  x.factors.filter (fun n => n % 2 = 1) |>.maximum.get_or_else 1
